WEBVTT

00:01.242 --> 00:03.031
In the criminal justice system

00:03.098 --> 00:04.592
sexually-based offenses

00:04.666 --> 00:06.160
are considered especially heinous.

00:06.587 --> 00:08.921
In New York City,
the dedicated detectives...

00:08.986 --> 00:10.513
who investigate these vicious felonies

00:10.587 --> 00:12.048
are members of an elite squad

00:12.123 --> 00:14.033
known as the Special Victims Unit.

00:14.107 --> 00:15.383
These are their stories.

00:18.331 --> 00:20.754
Tag and bag as soon as
the detectives are through.

00:20.827 --> 00:22.169
She's been
out here long enough.

00:22.236 --> 00:24.887
What's up, Doc?
Veronica Tandy...

00:24.956 --> 00:28.251
34 years old, stabbed in
the back, raped from behind.

00:28.349 --> 00:30.453
Any fluids?
Not that I can see.

00:30.525 --> 00:33.208
We'll swab. Hopefully,
find traces with the Luma.

00:33.660 --> 00:35.484
I've got a domestic
homicide mid-town...

00:35.550 --> 00:37.939
so I've scheduled the autopsy
later this afternoon.

00:38.014 --> 00:39.869
Don't be late.
Don't be late.

00:41.822 --> 00:43.764
She's got
a bruise on her neck.

00:43.839 --> 00:45.269
She was yoked.

00:45.694 --> 00:49.078
External examination
found no traces of semen.

00:49.759 --> 00:51.253
Further testing...

00:51.327 --> 00:55.190
showed spermicides
usually found in condoms.

00:55.456 --> 00:56.732
This is fun.

00:57.759 --> 00:58.807
Damn.

00:59.007 --> 01:00.088
Problem?

01:00.865 --> 01:03.899
Single fetus present,
seven to eight weeks.

01:04.610 --> 01:06.398
That'll probably
get suppressed at trial.

01:06.465 --> 01:08.668
According to the law,
a fetus is not a person.

01:08.737 --> 01:12.797
The stab wound was 2 inches wide,
8 inches deep, one edge serrated.

01:13.665 --> 01:14.746
That's a big knife.

01:14.819 --> 01:17.153
Cause of death?
Cardiopulmonary failure.

01:17.218 --> 01:20.383
The blade entered the back between
the ribs, collapsing the left lung.

01:20.450 --> 01:21.727
Takes care of any screaming.

01:22.851 --> 01:24.280
Could you grab that?

01:25.667 --> 01:26.682
Morgue.

01:27.811 --> 01:28.988
Be right out.

01:29.667 --> 01:31.523
Husband's here to ID the body.

01:33.636 --> 01:34.880
Mr. Tandy?

01:36.100 --> 01:38.849
I'm Det. Benson
from the Special Victims Unit.

01:39.493 --> 01:40.921
Are you alone?

01:42.373 --> 01:43.682
It's a mistake.

01:45.030 --> 01:47.134
My wife isn't here.

01:48.293 --> 01:49.887
Mr. Tandy...

01:57.255 --> 01:58.913
She's supposed to be home.

01:58.983 --> 02:02.332
She's supposed to be home!
She's supposed to be home!

